{
  "title": "Rectangle",
  "description": "Mutable axis-aligned rectangle defined by a top-left origin `(x, y)` and dimensions `(width, height)`. Implements ShapeLike with full SAT collision response for rectangles and polygons, and specialised algorithms for circle and ellipse intersections. `Rectangle.temp` is a shared scratch instance. Edge normals are lazily computed and cached; they are invalidated when position or size mutates.",
